<div className="grid grid-cols-2 h-[100%] "> <div className=" flex flex-row grow justify-center items-end gap-4 h-96"> <span className="bg-emerald-500 text-white border-indigo-500 border w-[calc(100%/14)] h-[20%] "> 1 </span> <span className="bg-blue-400 text-white border-indigo-500 border w-[calc(100%/14)] h-[40%]"> 2 </span> <span className="bg-yellow-200 text-white border-indigo-500 border w-[calc(100%/14)] h-[76%] "> 3 </span> <span className="bg-red text-white border-indigo-500 border w-[calc(100%/14)] h-[80%] "> 4 </span> </div> <div className=" grid-rows-2 gap-11 grid content-between "> <ul className="grid-cols-1 list-decimal"> <li className="text-3xl font-normal tracking-tight ml-8 text-white sm:text-3xl"> teste1 </li> <li className="text-3xl font-normal tracking-tight ml-8 text-white sm:text-3xl"> teste 2 </li> <li className="text-3xl font-normal tracking-tight ml-8 text-white sm:text-3xl"> teste 3 </li> <li className="text-3xl font-normal tracking-tight ml-8 text-white sm:text-3xl"> teste 4 </li> </ul> <div className=" grid items-center "> <h2 className="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl"> Faça parte disso </h2> </div> </div> </div> </section> ); }
